These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: parkour, golf, volleyball
1. Sport:golf is on the right of Sport:volleyball##1
2. Sport:parkour is on the far right##1
3. Sport:parkour is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | volleyball | golf | parkour |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: kiwi, cranberry, plum
1. Food:cranberry is in an odd position##4
2. Food:kiwi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | kiwi | plum | cranberry |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: photography, writing, puzzles
1. Hobby:writing is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:writing is on the left or right of Hobby:puzzles##3
3. Hobby:puzzles is on the right of Hobby:writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | photography | writing | puzzles |

 #################################
 
